---
title: Lamb Curry with Basmati Rice and Toasted Coconut
description: So many flavours and textures to sing the praises of in this dish, you'll wish there was more of it! Tender sweet zucchini, aromatic masla are perfectly complemented by sweet peas, toasted coconut and cilantro!
